open-opticon

This project is an overlay on OP-TEE remote attestation
(github.com/iisec-suzaki/optee-ra), which is distributed under its own
BSD-2-Clause license.

The embedded P-256 key in src/common/he_testkey.h is a published, non-secret
test key from that upstream project for the QEMU path only. It is not a
production secret.
